:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504113001: Config/Level/Mission/5041130/Act/Act504113001.json-->
:'''Livia:''' Where did that butterfly go... Oh, I know you! You're Phainon's friend!
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504113001_8-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504113001_8-->
